The African National Congress has noted media reports that the organization's 54th National Conference will be held in Kimberly, Northern Cape. This information is incorrect. The 54th National Conference will take place from the 16th to the 20th December 2017 in Gauteng.An inconvenience or confusion that may have been caused is regrettedIssued by the African National Congress Enquiries Zizi Kodwa 082 330 4910 National Spokesperson Khusela Sangoni 072 854 5707 National Communications Manager 